item.title: CUBE Player
item.description: When you’re playing music at your store, there is always equipment responsible for doing the playback, outputting the audio signal into your amplifier and speakers. Either you’re using a physical player device, like CUBE, or you’re running software on a phone, tablet or computer. In any case, there is always some piece of equipment involved.
